Class HuffmanNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • TreeNode
      • HuffmanNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<HuffmanNode>

    public class HuffmanNode
extends TreeNode
implements java.util.Comparator<HuffmanNode>
    A Huffman based node extension of the TreeNode and implementation of the Comparator interface.
